        <br>
        <h1 class="border-bottom text-center">General Guidelines</h1>

        <br><br>
        
        
        <h2 class="border-bottom">1. ARTIST CRITERIA & SELECTION</h2>
        <p>All artwork must be original and hand-made by the applicant or with the use of appropriate tools. Table must include original artwork. No additional items may be sold (i.e. water, candy, etc.).</p>
        <p>Any food items should be limited to the Foods Not Requiring a Food License as outlined in the <a href="https://agr.mt.gov/_docs/farmersmarket-docs/Farmers-Market-Portal-docs/ManagerResources/2020FARMERSMARKETguidelines.pdf" target="_blank">Farmers Market Guidelines.</a></p>
        

        <br>

        <h2 class="border-bottom">2. SALES TAX</h2>
        <p>All vendors are responsible for collecting and paying Arkansas State Sales Tax as applicable to their product.</p>

        <br>

        <h2 class="border-bottom">3. COST</h2>
        <p>Participation in this marketplace is free and limited to UARK graduate students. All proceeds go to the creators of the products.</p>

        <br>

        <h2 class="border-bottom">4. NOTIFICATION OF MARKET CANCELLATION</h2>
        <p>UARK GSMM will post all cancellations due to inclement weather or other circumstances on UARK GSMM website and social media pages.</p>

        <br>

        <h2 class="border-bottom">5. MARKET LOGISTICS</h2>
        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
            <li class="list-group-item" style="background-color: aliceblue;">Check-in will be from 2pm - 2:50 pm. Vendors must sign in and be ready to sell by 3 pm. Teardown is at 6 pm.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item" style="background-color: aliceblue;">Vendors are responsible for providing their own set up excluding tables and chairs. Access to electricity will be provided. Set up may not exceed provided table length. Space is available on a first come, first served basis. Spaces are not assigned except in the case of produce and agricultural product vendors.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item" style="background-color: aliceblue;">Parking: Please follow UARK parking guidelines. Harmon garage has paid public parking.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item" style="background-color: aliceblue;">Trash: Vendors are responsible for removal of all trash from vending space.</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <i>If you have any questions please contact us at <u>gsmm.uark@gmail.com</u></i>
